        <options>
            <option letter="a">He commanded Arctic exploration</option>
            <option letter="b">He led naval operations in the Philippines</option>
            <option letter="c">He developed naval technology</option>
            <option letter="d">He negotiated with Japan</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Admiral George Dewey led crucial naval operations in the Philippines, becoming a naval hero and the first U.S. Admiral of the Navy, symbolizing America's growing naval power.</explanation>
